## 🧠 Explainable AI (Grad-CAM)  

The system uses **Grad-CAM (Gradient-weighted Class Activation Mapping)** to:

- Highlight important regions in the image  
- Detect manipulation areas like:
  - Face boundaries  
  - Eyes and mouth regions  
  - Texture inconsistencies  
- Provide human-understandable explanations  

---

