## ⚙️ How It Works  

1. User uploads an image or uses webcam  
2. Image is preprocessed (resize, normalize, face crop)  
3. Selected model performs prediction  
4. Probability scores are calculated  
5. Grad-CAM highlights suspicious regions  
6. Final result with explanation is displayed  

